<Base>
    <h1>Arizona Field Ornithologists</h1>
    <div>
        <p>
            AZFO is an organization of birders dedicated to increasing the
            knowledge of the changing status, identification, and distribution
            of Arizona's birdlife. You can participate in our programs, peruse
            our online journal articles, and get involved in our mission. AZFO
            is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization.
        </p>
        <p>
            <a href="/about">Learn More</a>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <h2>News / Upcoming Events</h2>
        <div>
            <h3>New Field Expedition</h3>
            <time>May 13 - June 2</time>
            <p>
                Announcing a new Field Expedition to look for breeding Mountain
                Plovers! We will head out to a grassland area near
                Springerville, AZ.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3>2024 Annual Meeting</h3>
            <time>September 26-29</time>
            <p>
                <a
                    href="https://sites.google.com/azgfd.gov/azfowbbajam2024/home"
                    >Registration is now open!</a
                >
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
